About:
Search Engine
Parse XML->Tokenization->Case Folding->StopWord Removal->Stemming ->Posting List / Inverted Index Creation

To Run:
sudo bash ./install.sh

./index path/to/file.xml  path/to/index/folder

./query path/to/index/folder 
